{"tid":829051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「轉數快」轉錯帳滙豐收250元 轉賬交易要留神 取消交易須額外付費","createTime":"2018-09-20T06:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T09:52:37.000Z","uid":113000,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bc326e6e3f98737d84fd4dd617d86f723217d08c","tid":829051,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"【FinTech理財】轉賬交易要留神　取消交易須額外付費<br />\n即時財經13:34 2018/09/20<br />\n<br />\n金管局推出「轉數快」系統，各大銀行亦迅速配合於17日正式接受用戶登記，大部分銀行使用跨行轉帳均豁免收費。但要留意，某些情況下如轉錯錢，部分銀行都會向客戶收取額外服務費。<span style=\"color: red;\">如滙豐銀行，若客戶取消交易指示，每次會向客戶收取250元費用。</span><br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人接受本網查詢時表示，上述額外徵收的費用，並非因「轉數快」推出而新增的，是該行固有的措施。<span style=\"color: red;\">如客戶轉錯帳給其他人而要取消付款指令，滙豐每次會收取250元。而因戶口結餘不足而退回款項的話，每次會收取150元費用。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://invest.hket.com/article/2164922/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2164922%2F&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cw%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6007c4db\" target=\"_blank\">https://invest.hket.com/article/2164922/</a>"},{"pid":"647a1f5903a9859e8cfe9fa02a76de0f37de7234","tid":829051,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .....<br />\n叫驚青既人可以唔洗用"},{"pid":"5ef6c651007d98b96e946f1314cef7a79079c9a8","tid":829051,"uid":19557,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"屌 轉錯要比250 好過借貸喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a10cf4accdc11b75ad41383ad9335943faaaa31","tid":829051,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"ATM繼續塞死一班過數狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ea7539d7848628bf75a3011d1419a3e36f6afe","tid"